                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "You hear that? The walls. The walls are FULL of nincada, and one day they will all shed at once and it will be BEAUTIFUL. Bug Maniac Shin. Second floor. No refunds."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Surskit skates on water. Nincada digs through stone. Between them there is nowhere you can stand. I have thought about this a lot."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Shin — the walls are full",
                    Label: "default"
                }
